<section id="bottom_cta">
    <div id="bottom_cta_content">
        <h2 id="bottom_cta_content_title">READY TO RESTORE YOUR VEHICLE?</h2>
        <p>Don’t let damage keep you off the road any longer. Trust the experts at Northern Beaches Smash Repairs to bring your car back to its best. Whether you need a quick fix or a full restoration, we’re here to help.</p>
